{"tid":1291096,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開/以智取勝] 7/7打算以暴易暴嘅手足，希望你入嚟睇一睇","createTime":"2019-07-06T17:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T17:37:54.000Z","uid":274813,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"41a2d5b85242a30d5eb490ace9090753ad6aae2a","tid":1291096,"uid":274813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:33:59.000Z","msg":"頭先撳錯制 唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先多謝肯撳入嚟睇嘅你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始見到有post主張聽日以暴易暴，我明，我諗全部香港人都好明你地係有幾嬲。<br />\n<br />\n但係，聽日絕對唔係一個適合暴力嘅時間。點解? 最重要嘅原因只有一個<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>黑警選擇性執法</ins></strong><br />\n經過呢一個多月，相信黑警嘅做法有幾污穢，幾仆街，大家有目共睹。由當初扮拖人入暗巷再放行，到今日光復屯門公園係幾廿支cam面前直接開路送條藍絲上車。<br />\n<br />\n咁代表咩?<br />\n咁代表黑警已經唔會在乎自己成為全民公敵。聽日啲狗都會做返一模一樣嘅事。你同班忠義撚屌互抽，警犬都會照係鏡頭面前選擇性執法。你會照被塔返狗屋，而班撚屌? 坐的士返屋企沖涼大教瞓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住，今次運動同五大訴求一樣重要嘅信條:<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 一個都不能少，不流血，不被捕</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>!</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nQ: 咁你個P牌仔踩住高地想點撚樣啊? 俾人打都唔撚還拖啊下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>冇撚可能!</strong></span><br />\nKnow your strengths. 我地嘅優勢係咩? <strong><ins>人數</ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我地做我地最擅長嘅事:<strong><ins>圍</ins></strong><br />\n藍絲可以混入嚟嘅原因就係我地人數多，正係咁佢地覺得可以掩人耳目咁打人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正是如此，一個人搞事，一百個人圍鳩佢。俾一堆人海咁圍，我諗冇咩人仲可以惡得出。<br />\n你睇下當年大波man，一樣俾人圍到鵪鶉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/R7WKH7wQRRU?t=129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FR7WKH7wQRRU%3Ft%3D129&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR3f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=b704a044\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/R7WKH7wQRRU?t=129</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸一下，<strong><ins>cam好緊要</ins></strong>。cam未必可以即時保護到你，更加嚇唔到黑警。<br />\n但係cam絕對可以保護到你<strong><ins>唔俾人秋後算帳</ins></strong>。<br />\n呢個白色恐怖嘅環境教識左我地一樣野: <strong><ins>開個cam可能比你袋把刀更能夠保護自己</ins></strong><br />\n就算出事嘅唔係你，你支cam都可以救到同路人一命，甚至可以係文宣嘅子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次開post打到1999咁，仲要唔係啲咩新嘅idea sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到老土都係個句: <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Be Water</span>，香港人只要做到shapeless，一定可以笑到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日，九龍見"},{"pid":"b453144b18052e2fd47d1696539901ef98e32a2d","tid":1291096,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:34:40.000Z","msg":"P牌仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e95beb200e4f8514e21f78c31db39582e040284","tid":1291096,"uid":251414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 畀人打完一樣要畀人拉， 已負皮</span></span>"},{"pid":"90c73bf4b05713e629b012eaba5611fb6f18ad59","tid":1291096,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:36:11.000Z","msg":"同意人多就係我哋嘅優勢<br />\n<br />\n________<br />\n黑衫口罩作記認<br />\n一. 可以掩飾身份<br />\n二. 響街度可以幫返自己人<br />\n<br />\n「七黑」團結打倒白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284973\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284973</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zm1ytZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzm1ytZc.jpg&h=68603869&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c33f2782add1799a380b076aa90f22fff233